<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287941>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Penis in ventral, lateral and dorsal view of apex of the species Calligrapha simillima Stål (a, d), C. sylvia Stål (b, e), C. diversa Stål (c, f), C. aeneopicta Stål (g, h), and C. elegantula Jacoby (i, j). Scale bar = 0.5 mm." ;
